2. Set Interface
Features

✅ No duplicates

❌ No indexing

Implementations
HashSet
LinkedHashSet
TreeSet
Example
import java.util.*;

public class Demo {

    public static void main(String[] args) {

        Set<String> set = new HashSet<>();

        set.add("Java");
        set.add("Python");
        set.add("Java");

        System.out.println(set);
    }
}

Output

[Java, Python]
