3. Queue Interface
Features

✅ FIFO (First In First Out)

Example
import java.util.*;

public class Demo {

    public static void main(String[] args) {

        Queue<Integer> q = new LinkedList<>();

        q.add(10);
        q.add(20);
        q.add(30);

        System.out.println(q.poll());
    }
}

Output

10
Queue Diagram
Front                    Rear

[10] → [20] → [30]

poll()

[20] → [30]
